0.2.name: wordpress/easy-tynt
0.2.description:
Easily install and configure Tynt Insight for your WordPress Blog. Leverage the benefit of copy/paste, learn what is being copied off your blog, and learn how to leverage this behavior into more traffic, higher search rank and more. See http://www.tynt.com for information on Tynt Insight.

If you like Easy Tynt, please visit it on WordPress.org's Plugin Area and rate it.
